{"tid":1800372,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩電影關於美國獨立戰爭?","createTime":"2019-12-27T17:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T11:05:55.000Z","uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c9848bbf39ff4ff53bf03e16b588164dd63fd3","tid":1800372,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf19a01200fed1ef36bd400bbc997a36e0bc759","tid":1800372,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"在1760年代和1770年代，13個北美殖民地與英國之間的關係趨於緊張，導<span style=\"color: red;\">致1774年與1775年的一連串武裝衝突</span>。出席第二屆大陸會議的13個殖民地的代表們在1776年7月4日簽下《美國獨立宣言》，使得武裝衝突轉化為獨立戰爭，代表們並於會中決議創立大陸軍以對抗英軍，由喬治&middot;華盛頓領導[51]。1781年，《邦聯條例》獲得13個構成州的全數同意，一個永久性邦聯成立。在法國和西班牙幫助下，<span style=\"color: red;\">經歷艱苦的8年獨立戰爭後</span>，大陸軍團終於擊敗英軍，使得英國於1783年簽下《巴黎條約》，正式承認13個北美殖民地的獨立。1787年的制憲會議，提出了一部使邦聯轉變成聯邦體制的憲法，1789年6月，這部《美利堅合眾國憲法》獲得13個州中的9個州批准生效<br />\n<br />\n打左8年⋯⋯"},{"pid":"4465e6bfb88891dcc9d0cec0f3949cf3f02e5597","tid":1800372,"uid":179935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"Patriots-Mel Gibson做"},{"pid":"027fcc5c34347889b42de1778f11eb49e79c7507","tid":1800372,"uid":202362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:49:06.000Z","msg":"The patriot<br />\n但從Mel Gibson拍過有關人民反抗嘅戰爭片嚟講 Braveheart最高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係講蘇格蘭人反抗英格蘭"},{"pid":"8cd7a65b356b52a58376240927fde5f145179beb","tid":1800372,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4465e6bfb88891dcc9d0cec0f3949cf3f02e5597","tid":1800372,"uid":179935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"Patriots-Mel Gibson做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d7c52d0c04b856c146c7a25d33c234e3d5393e